{"tid":2342812,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【呀~~柒娥要飛往天上】 林婆乘坐直升機俯瞰視察各區情況","createTime":"2020-12-27T12:06:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T12:14:55.000Z","uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f51e582f4ce095f951e5b80057037a68b2582325","tid":2342812,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥今日（十二月二十七日）在保安局局長李家超及發展局局長黃偉綸陪同下，到訪政府飛行服務隊總部，並乘坐直升機視察多項她在《2020年施政報告》中提出的發展計畫。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說：「隨著香港融入國家發展大局，加強與深圳合作，我們會充分考慮如何善用邊境地區或跨境基建附近地點的地理優勢，以把握粵港澳大灣區帶來的種種機遇。」"},{"pid":"943e5e11b4e850957285aa347d6a6ab4e6da5c24","tid":2342812,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rooCBwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrooCBwW.jpg&h=333ec392&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db3a2eff01533faf87414618b7dc513d53b62973","tid":2342812,"uid":7323,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:07:55.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">屌你老母，快撚d死</span>"},{"pid":"5838dfdb97e48435c4112fc7ac45d8cf22f25e8a","tid":2342812,"uid":289708,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"點解冇帶佢最鐘意果個銅芯抗疫口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa745274cfd46ab2b11703c06d3eeb211dd6570","tid":2342812,"uid":99962,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:08:27.000Z","msg":"真.堅離地"},{"pid":"c8c7dc97e91ea9321ed9149db952e85ce621ce5e","tid":2342812,"uid":182334,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"點解係kobe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aabf994b5f8c2f56f9eea86a7c1a9bd22d0f7e6","tid":2342812,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T12:09:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAbkyUv.jpg&amp;h=1